The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻记者 汤琪国家卫健委专家组成员、北京地坛医院感染科主任医师蒋荣猛。
Peng Pai journalist Tang Qi National Health Committee expert group member, Beijing Ditan Hospital infection department chief physician Jiang Rong Meng.
澎湃新闻记者 汤琪 图3月5日下午，北京支援武汉医疗队在武汉协和医院西院区举行京汉两地远程重症病例讨论，交流重症患者救治和医院感染工作经验。
BEIJING SUPPORT FOR WUHAN MEDICAL TEAM IN WUHANG HAI WESTERN WUHAN CITY WESTERN hospital on the afternoon of March 5, 2007.
澎湃新闻（www.thepaper.cn）从会上了解到，目前，北京医疗队主要负责武汉协和医院西院区8楼、10楼和12楼病区。
At present, the medical team in Beijing is mainly responsible for the sick areas on the 8th, 10th and 12th floors of the WESTERN Campus of Wuhan Concord Hospital, according to the conference.
截止3月3日，累计收治患者突破300例，累计收治重症患者78例，累计出院68例。
As of March 3, the total number of patients admitted to more than 300, a total of 78 patients received serious illness, cumulative discharge from the hospital 68.
作为国家卫健委专家组成员，北京地坛医院感染科主任医师蒋荣猛早在1月9日就来到武汉指导新冠肺炎疫情防控工作，坚守至今已超过50天，成为在武汉指导工作时间最长的专家之一。
As a member of the national health committee, Beijing Ditan Hospital infection director Jiang Rong came to Wuhan as early as January 9 to guide the prevention and control of the disease, has been more than 50 days, becoming one of the longest-serving experts in Wuhan.
蒋荣猛在会上表示，新冠肺炎是一个自限性疾病，没有有效的抗病毒药物，反而有很多抗病毒药物在临床上引起了很多副作用，因此，应以不损害病人为先，尽可能考虑病人的副作用、能不能耐受等问题。
At the meeting, Jiang Rong said that pneumonia was a self-limited disease with no effective antiviral drugs. Instead, many anti-viral drugs had caused many side effects clinically. Therefore, the patient's side effects and tolerance should be considered as far as possible without harming the patient.
针对激素使用，蒋荣猛说，他前段时间和卞修武院士在讨论病理的时候了解到，新冠病毒总的来讲损害两个方面——免疫系统和肺，其他器官基本是继发性的缺氧引起来的。
In response to hormonal use, Jiang said he had learned from discussing pathology with academician Bian Xiuwu some time ago that the new crown virus in general damages the immune system and the lungs.
从一些病案看出，病人的脾脏和淋巴结“一片荒凉、寸草不生”，在这种情况下还用激素的话，病人的免疫功能是没办法恢复，使用激素千万要小心。
In some cases, the patient's spleen and lymph nodes are "desolate and barren," and if hormone is used in this case, the patient's immune function cannot be restored. Be careful when using hormones.
此外，很多重症病人离世以后，肺泡里、巨噬细胞里仍然有大量的新冠病毒。
In addition, after the death of many severe patients, alveoli, macrophages still have a large number of new canopy viruses.
“这也能解释很多病人在出院的时候病毒‘复阳’的情况，我们认为是病毒没有完全清除，咽拭子检测出现阴性只是假象，肺里仍然有病毒，这对于我们的防控工作会带来新的挑战。
"It also explains why a lot of patients get out of the hospital with the virus, which we think is not completely eliminated, negative pharyngeal swabs are false and there is still a virus in the lungs, which poses new challenges for our control efforts.
”他说。
'he said.
蒋荣猛会后在接受澎湃新闻采访时，进一步解释了当前备受关注的出院患者“复阳”问题。
Jiang Rong Meng in the wake of the Pai news interview, further explained the current concerns about discharged patients "Fuyang."
他表示，一些出现“复阳”的患者身体里的病毒并不是完全被清除了，核酸检测的敏感性是有限的。
He said the virus in some patients with "fuyang" had not been completely eliminated and the sensitivity of nucleic acid testing was limited.
“我们现在看到有些病人病毒检测呈阳性的时间可以超过30天，甚至超过40天。
"We now see patients who are HIV-positive for more than 30 days or more.
如果病人在前三周治疗后符合出院标准，但实际上他还有十几天、二十天（可能携带病毒），所以国家在第六版、第七版诊疗方案中要求出院后再隔离两周，避免和其他人接触，就是要防止病毒没有被完全清除的情况出现。
If the patient meets the discharge criteria after the first three weeks of treatment, but in fact he still has 10 days, 20 days (possibly carrying the virus), the State, in the sixth and seventh editions of the programme, requires isolation for a further two weeks to avoid contact with others, in order to prevent the virus from not being completely eliminated.
”不过，蒋荣猛也坦言，目前“复阳”的传播力有多大尚不清楚，因为阳性不一定是真病毒，有可能是病毒尸体或碎片，所以还要继续研究，看到底有没有传染性。
However, Jiang also admitted that it was not clear how widespread Fuyang was at the moment, because a positive might not be a real virus, but might be a viral corpse or fragment, so he would have to continue studying whether it was contagious.
此前的2月28日，国家卫健委医政医管局监察专员郭燕红在国务院联防联控机制新闻发布会上介绍，部分省报告治愈出院患者，在复诊过程中发现有核酸检测阳性的情况。
Earlier on February 28, Guo Yanhong, the National Health and Wellbeing Hospital Authority Ombudsman, told a news conference of the State Council's Joint Prevention and Control Mechanism that some provinces had reported that they had cured patients discharged from hospital and found nucleic acid positive during the revisits.
通过监测发现，这部分患者没有再发生传染别人的现象，另外有一部分患者再检测新冠病毒核酸时又转为阴性。
The surveillance found that this group of patients no longer infected with other people, and another part of the patients when the new crown virus nucleic acid test turned negative.
对于是否可用病毒抗体IgM与IgG的检查作为判断出院的手段，蒋荣猛告诉澎湃新闻，抗体检查与能不能出院没有关系，抗体和传染性无关，抗体检查只是作为补充诊断，一个人产生了抗体说明他感染了病毒。
Jiang told the roar news that the antibody test had nothing to do with the ability to leave the hospital. The antibody test had nothing to do with the ability to leave the hospital. The antibodies were not related to the infectivity.
在核酸检测不能百分之百检出来时，发现他有抗体了，就能做出诊断。
When the nucleic acid test was not 100% complete, he was found to have an antibody and was able to make a diagnosis.
